# @see docs/specs/400-dx-conventions/spec.md [FR-5]
#
# Setup once: git config commit.template .gitmessage
#

#

# Types: build | chore | ci | docs | feat | fix | perf | refactor | revert | style | test

#

# Scopes (required): chat | workbench | vscode | shared | parsers | ui |

# transport | pi | pi-sdk | workbench/notes | workbench/journal |

# workbench/board | workbench/pipeline | bottom-panel |

# deps | ci | release | docs | infra | dx | repo | spec

#

# Breaking change: add ! after scope, or add BREAKING CHANGE: footer

#

# Body (optional — blank line before):

#

#

# Footer (optional — blank line before):

# Co-Authored-By: Name <email>

# BREAKING CHANGE: description
